The example of how to use is [[Template talk:Football player statistics 1]].

==Template:Football player statistics 1==
===Parameter 1===
*NN=League, Cup
*NY=League, Cup, Continental
*YN=League, Cup, League Cup
*YY=League, Cup, League Cup, Continental

===Example===
<pre>{{Football player statistics 1|NN}}</pre>
or
<pre>{{Football player statistics 1|NY}}</pre>

==Template:Football player statistics 2==
===Parameter 1===
*The cord of the country

===Parameter 2===
*NN=League, Cup
*NY=League, Cup, Continental
*YN=League, Cup, League Cup
*YY=League, Cup, League Cup, Continental

===Example===
<pre>{{Football player statistics 2|ENG|NY}}</pre>
or
<pre>{{Football player statistics 2|BRA|YY}}</pre>

==Template:Football player statistics 3==
===Parameter 1===
*The number of countries

===Parameter 2===
*The cord of the country

===Example===
<pre>{{Football player statistics 3|2|SCO}}</pre>
or
<pre>{{Football player statistics 3|1|JPN}}</pre>

==Template:Football player statistics 4==
===Parameter 1===
*The cord of the country

===Example===
<pre>{{Football player statistics 4|ITA}}</pre>
or
<pre>{{Football player statistics 4|FRA}}</pre>

